snippet.textDisplay: I remember this song vividly. When I was doing my engineering, this song was the biggest hit in India for that whole year. This song was like the number one song for that whole year and was played in every function of the college. I saw the real singer - Hasan Jahangir today for the first time after like 2 decades. But the voice and singing, OMG, its epic. He is as good as he was that time. Kudos. Thank you Coke Studio Pakistan for bringing back my memories. This song still sounds so good, I can't believe it. Stood the test of time. Cheers.
